channel.title: Need help with logg in help options
channel.description:
Ok so u know how on all servers when u logg in it say something like ------------------------------------------------------------------
oh yea press ::haha to fuck ur mom! ::help ::modhelp
--------------------------------------------------------------------
how do i change that?
need help plz

Usually welcome messages say Welcome back or welcome to.

But just search public void initialize()

and scroll down alot, and you will find it.
